snippet.title: Zero Killed Release Date Announcement Gameplay Trailer (HTC Vive, Oculus Rift)
snippet.description:
SIGN UP FOR BETA NOW ◣ http://playzerokilled.com/beta

The Data Access Point has been located. Hacking Device is ready, the Attackers are in positions, and waiting for the signal. They need to make quick work of it... or die trying.

ENTER THE ZERO KILLED KEY GIVEAWAY ◣ https://gleam.io/6LJf4/zero-killed-giveaway

Zero Killed is an immersive, tactical VR multiplayer shooter.
Experience the next generation of battle in virtual reality with a tactical gameplay ensured by the use of various gadgets, weapons, items and team cooperation in September 2018. Join the beta testing now at http://playzerokilled.com/#beta
Coming to HTC Vive and Oculus Rift on Steam September 26th 2018.
